\f0\b Discover authentic local experiences\'a0
\f1\b0 \

\f0\b A UX design study focusing on user research and usability testing
\f1\b0 \

\f0\b Project overview
\f1\b0 \

\f0\b Summary:
\f1\b0 \
Through qualitative and quantitative user research, I discovered that travelers have a difficult time finding information about local experiences available at their desired destinations. This reality causes them to miss authentic experiences and to waste time and money once they are at their destination.\
PukkaTrip is a travel app prototype designed to alleviate the described pain point by helping travelers discover authentic local experiences.\'a0\
