\f1\b0 \
Finding a user insight was my first step to begin defining the problem space and give the user a face and a voice. This user insight summarizes opinions given by multiple people during the user research phase.\'a0\
Before and while they travel, travelers need access to information about local activities and authentic food available at their destination to have unique experiences while maximizing their time and budget.\

