\f0\b A challenge
\f1\b0 \
At this point in the ideation process, I realized that integrating a poll feature that allows users to post questions and receive individualized responses would address the user\'92s pain points and make it stand out from competitors.\'a0\
However, a poll feature requires users to engage with the app by responding to other travelers\'92 polls, which makes the functionality sustainable and keeps the information authentic. Answering to other users' questions is a big ask that could deter some potential users from using the app.\'a0\
To move forward, I took a close look at the user persona and concluded that a poll feature would be well adopted by my user based on the following assumptions.\'a0\

