\ls10\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
The user is willing to take extra steps to make sure he gets the information he needs to maximize his travel experience\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

