\ls11\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Replying to a poll has to be as effortless as possible. Language in the request should be carefully crafted to incentivize its use and boost user\'92s buy-in\
